<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found – Super Sonic</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --gold:#F9D342;--bg:#050505;--text:#EAEAEA;--text-dim:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
        * { margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box; }
        body { font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:40px; }
        .wrap { max-width:520px; }
        .code { font-size:clamp(72px,12vw,120px);font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);line-height:1;margin-bottom:16px; }
        h1 { font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px; }
        p { font-size:15px;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:32px; }
        a { display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 32px;background:var(--gold);color:#000;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;border-radius:60px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .25s; }
        a:hover { background:#fff;transform:translateY(-2px); }
        a svg { width:14px;height:14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="code">404</div>
        <h1>Page not found.</h1>
        <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved. Let's get you back on track.</p>
        <a href="/">
            Back to Home
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 13L13 3M13 3H5M13 3v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
